    public interface DataStructure
extends java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Defines the interface, all classes, which represent a data structure, must implement. Such data structures therefore must implement the interface Serializable to support serialization, as well as the interface Cloneable, to allow deep copies of class instances.
    Since:
    0.1.0
